			<div id="post-2296" class="post-2296 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-opera-cake category-pastry">
			<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="meta-prep meta-prep-author"></span> <a href="http://www.joepastry.com/2009/coffee_cake_syrup_recipe/" title="8:41 pm" rel="bookmark"><span class="entry-date">10/05/09</span></a> <span class="meta-sep"></span> <span class="author vcard" style="display:none;"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.joepastry.com/author/joepastry/" title="View all posts by joepastry">joepastry</a></span>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
            
            
            <h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://www.joepastry.com/2009/coffee_cake_syrup_recipe/" title="Permalink to Coffee-Flavored Cake Syrup Recipe" rel="bookmark">Coffee-Flavored Cake Syrup Recipe</a></h2>

				<div class="entry-content">
				<p>This is just standard cake syrup but with a little zing. Remember that cake syrup is made by combining water and sugar  2-1 by volume and then heating it until the sugar dissolves. To make coffee cake syrup combine 1 cup of water with half a cup of sugar and add about three tablespoons of instant coffee or instant espresso powder. Bring the mixture to a simmer and&#8230;done! Cool and store in the refrigerator until needed. It&#8217;ll keep well for a week or more. </p>
                			</div><!-- .entry-summary -->
	
			<div class="entry-utility">
									<span class="cat-links">
						<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-cat-links">Filed under:&nbsp;</span> <a href="http://www.joepastry.com/category/pastry/opera-cake/" title="View all posts in Opera Cake" rel="category tag">Opera Cake</a>, <a href="http://www.joepastry.com/category/pastry/" title="View all posts in Pastry" rel="category tag">Pastry</a>					</span>
					<span class="meta-sep">|</span>
								                <span class="comments-link"><a href="http://www.joepastry.com/2009/coffee_cake_syrup_recipe/#comments" title="Comment on Coffee-Flavored Cake Syrup Recipe">6 Comments</a></span>
